{"tid":979394,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個係咪某定律?","createTime":"2019-01-12T16:01:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T17:38:30.000Z","uid":91909,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ae4db56bd196df2528fa4d9c3987d72b4adb28df","tid":979394,"uid":91909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T16:01:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">玩家A</span> vs <span style=\"color: gold;\">玩家B</span><br />\n<br />\nA放 2紅波入箱<br />\nB放 4黃波入箱<br />\n<br />\n抽一個，抽中隻色 = 贏<br />\n<br />\n勝率：<br />\nA = 2/6 = 33.3%<br />\nB = 4/6 = 66.6%<br />\n<br />\n如果大家同時加一樣數量既波入箱，例如各加4個<br />\n<br />\n勝率：<br />\nA = 6/14 = 42.8%<br />\nB = 8/14= 57.1%<br />\n<br />\n當兩邊不斷加同樣數量既波入去，弱既一方會不斷增加勝算，呢一個有冇一種定律?"},{"pid":"02a0bd04f3ca67be04c248cf77db539bee854a08","tid":979394,"uid":125976,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"ae4db56bd196df2528fa4d9c3987d72b4adb28df","tid":979394,"uid":91909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T16:01:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">玩家A</span> vs <span style=\"color: gold;\">玩家B</span><br />\n<br />\nA放 2紅波入箱<br />\nB放 4黃波入箱<br />\n<br />\n抽一個，抽中隻色 = 贏<br />\n<br />\n勝率：<br />\nA = 2/6 = 33.3%<br />\nB = 4/6 = 66.6%<br />\n<br />\n如果大家同時加一樣數量既波入箱，例如各加4個<br />\n<br />\n勝率：<br />\nA = 6/14 = 42.8%<br />\nB = 8/14= 57.1%<br />\n<br />\n當兩邊不斷加同樣數量既波入去，弱既一方會不斷增加勝算，呢一個有冇一種定律?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T16:18:06.000Z","msg":"有，叫概率 (Probability)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d443d81ccfd0be4ac99ee315d408af39a74caee3","tid":979394,"uid":7438,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T16:21:05.000Z","msg":"Limit啫，當加得越多，開頭個差額嘅影響力就越細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca2c83f74a9d482b63bd3b696aac32177a15c012","tid":979394,"uid":189638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T16:22:39.000Z","msg":"唔明你想問乜<br />\n<br />\n但 A 嘅贏率係 ： 4N-2 / 8N-2<br />\